data.description: MOTIVATED SELLERS:  Why wait months to build a new home when you can buy this move-in ready almost new home located on nearly acre wooded lot with stream on culdesac in small Pickens subdivision; close to schools, grocery, and restaurants.  Better than new 3 bedroom, 2 bath, plus finished bonus room;  featuring open floor and split bedroom plan; stacked stone gas log fireplace, upgraded granite countertops, soft-close cabinets doors and drawers, luxury vinyl flooring in all downstairs.  Cathedral ceiling and light walls makes for an inviting atmosphere.  Private master bedroom and features ensuite bath with huge walk-in shower.  Men will love the oversized garage and 2nd driveway leading to a separate covered boat/car shed around back.  Overlook that area from the covered rear porch.  Or enjoy afternoons rocking on the front porch.  Bonus room great for 4th bedroom, man cave, craft room, or kid’s play room.  Come take a look and fall in love with this beautiful home
